==="These Are The Voyages..." (2005)===
{{multiple image
| footer    = Jonathan Frakes and Marina Sirtis returned to their ''The Next Generation'' roles for the series finale of ''Enterprise''.
 | image1    = Jonathan Frakes cropped1.jpg
